'''史蒂芬·加汉'''（{{lang-en|Stephen Gaghan}}，{{bd|1965年|5月6日}}）是一名美国男[[编剧|编剧]]和[[电影导演|导演]]<ref name=NYT1>{{cite web|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|title=Stephen Gaghan|url=http://www.nytimes.com/movies/person/277095/Stephen-Gaghan|accessdate=2014-04-09|archive-date=2014-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140318140526/http://www.nytimes.com/movies/person/277095/Stephen-Gaghan|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他编剧的由[[史蒂文·索德伯格|史蒂文·索德伯格]]导演的2000年[[毒品|毒品]]电影《[[毒品网络|毒品网络]]》<ref name=NYT1/>赢得[[奥斯卡最佳改编剧本奖|奥斯卡最佳改编剧本奖]]<ref>{{cite web|work=[[Indiewire|Indiewire]]|date=June 24, 2013|title=How One Writer Turned a Love for Writing Into an Oscar- and Emmy-Award Winning Career|url=http://www.indiewire.com/article/how-one-writer-turned-a-love-for-writing-into-an-oscar-and-emmy-award-winning-carer-exclusive-excerpt-from-traffic-screenwriter-stephen-gaghan|first=Stephen|last=Gaghan|accessdate=2014-04-09|archive-date=2014-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140308073238/http://www.indiewire.com/article/how-one-writer-turned-a-love-for-writing-into-an-oscar-and-emmy-award-winning-carer-exclusive-excerpt-from-traffic-screenwriter-stephen-gaghan|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此外，他执导和编剧的2005年[[石油|石油]]题材的《[[辛瑞那|辛瑞那]]》获得[[奥斯卡最佳原创剧本奖|奥斯卡最佳原创剧本奖]]提名。

==个人生活==
加汉与前女友、女演员Michael McCraine育有一个儿子 Gardner (1999年) 和一个女儿Elizabeth (2001年) <ref name=NYT3/>。2007年5月19日，他与服装设计师[[Minnie_Mortimer|Minnie Mortimer]]结婚<ref name=NYT3>{{cite web|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2007/05/27/fashion/weddings/27VOWS.html|first=William|last=L. Hamilton|date=May 27, 2007|title=Stephen Gaghan and Minnie Mortimer|accessdate=2014-04-09|archive-date=2013-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131107182311/http://www.nytimes.com/2007/05/27/fashion/weddings/27VOWS.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2009年2月2日女儿出生<ref>{{cite web |author=Minnie Mortimer |url=http://guestofaguest.com/directory/minnie-mortimer/ |title=Minnie Mortimer |publisher=Guest of a Guest |date= |accessdate=November 15, 2012 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121028113211/http://guestofaguest.com/directory/minnie-mortimer/ |archivedate=2012年10月28日 }}</ref>。

